results.name: Jordan 2 Retro Italy (GS)
results.story: Made for big kids, the Air Jordan 2 Retro GS ‘Origins’ gets dressed in a color scheme that references the silhouette’s continental provenance. (The original 1986 launch paired premium materials with made-in-Italy craftsmanship.) Built with smooth white leather, the upper retains the lizard-textured overlay of the OG AJ2. The midfoot panel is surrounded by red and green piping, with the contrasting hues making repeat appearances on the shoe’s heel and interior lining. Branding elements include a Nike wordmark on the back tab and an embossed Wings logo on the tongue. Anchoring the sneaker is an off-white foam midsole with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning.

results.name: Jordan 2 Retro Italy (TD)
results.story: Scaled down for little feet, the Air Jordan 2 Retro TD ‘Origins’ spotlights a distinctive palette that nods to the model’s 1986 debut. (In a marked departure from the shoe’s predecessor, the original AJ2 combined an elegant Swooshless design with made-in-Italy craftsmanship.) The legacy silhouette sports a white leather upper with a lizard-textured midfoot overlay outlined in red and green piping. The latter hue makes a repeat appearance on the heel counter, while Fire Red accents land on the interior lining, Nike-branded back tab, and the retro Wings logo embossed on the tongue. A cushy foam midsole features an off-white finish for a vintage aesthetic.

results.name: Jordan 2 Retro Italy (PS)
results.story: Made for little kids, the Air Jordan 2 Retro PS ‘Origins’ features accent colors inspired by the shoe’s premium ‘80s roots. The legacy silhouette makes use of a white leather upper with a lizard-textured midfoot overlay outlined in red and green piping. Exterior branding elements are limited to an embossed Wings logo on the tongue and a Nike wordmark on the heel tab, both of which are rendered in a bold Fire Red finish. A contrasting hit of Fir Green lands on the heel counter. Anchoring the sneaker is a vintage off-white midsole built with cushy foam.

Jordan 5 Retro A Ma Maniére Dusk
results.story: The A Ma Maniére x Air Jordan 5 Retro ‘Dusk’ reunites the creative partners on a two-piece collaborative pack. This pair carries a black nubuck upper, updated with a slimmed-down collar and pre-yellowed quarter panel netting formed with an interlocking series of A Ma Maniére’s signature ‘A’ logo. ‘Nike Air’ is embroidered on the back heel in tonal fashion, while silver reflective tongues display mismatched Jumpman and A Ma Maniére branding. The sneaker sits atop a matching black polyurethane midsole with shark-tooth detailing in a dark burgundy hue. A pre-aged translucent rubber outsole provides durable traction underfoot.

results.name: Dunk Low 'From Nike, To You - Gorge Green'
Jordan 13 Retro Wheat (2023)
results.story: The 2023 edition of the Air Jordan 13 Retro ‘Wheat’ brings back the retro colorway, first released in October 2004. Like the original, the upper features a smooth white leather forefoot, tonal dimpled leather overlays, and beige synthetic suede paneling that extends from the midfoot to the heel. Embroidered Jumpman branding graces the tongue, while the 13’s holographic eye adorns the lateral collar. Synthetic suede wraps the Phylon midsole, fitted with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning in the forefoot and heel, and supported by a panther paw rubber outsole underfoot.

results.name: Museum of Peace and Quiet x Classic Clog RO 'Mocha'
Jordan 2 Retro Low Chicago Twist (Women's)
results.story: The 2023 edition of the Women’s Air Jordan 2 Retro Low ‘Chicago’ brings back an OG colorway of Michael Jordan’s sophomore signature shoe. True to the original 1987 release, the low-top features a white leather upper with perforated detailing and a tonal midfoot overlay outlined in red piping. Matching crimson accents land on the molded back tab and the retro Wings logo atop the tongue. A solid black finish is applied to the polyurethane midsole, fitted with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning and reinforced by a two-tone rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 13 Retro Wheat (2023) (TD)
results.story: The 2023 edition of the Air Jordan 13 Retro TD ‘Wheat’ brings back a two-tone colorway in a scaled-down build made for little feet. The design is faithful to the original 2004 release, featuring white leather construction on the toe and dimpled overlays. Beige synthetic suede covers the heel and collar, which is marked with a holographic ‘eye’ on the lateral side. An embroidered Jumpman logo decorates the tongue. Anchoring the sneaker is a lightweight two-tone foam midsole.

results.name: Jordan 13 Retro Wheat (2023) (PS)
results.story: Built for little kids, the 2023 reissue of the Air Jordan 13 Retro PS ‘Wheat’ brings back a two-tone colorway from Jordan Brand’s 2004 archive. The upper features a white leather toe, matching the dimpled leather overlays that give the Air Jordan 13 its distinctive look. Beige suede wraps around the heel and collar, accented with a green-tinted ‘eye’ on the lateral side. Underfoot, a rubber panther-paw outsole features herringbone traction pods for superior grip.

results.name: Jordan 13 Retro Wheat (2023) (GS)
results.story: Made for big kids, the 2023 edition of the Air Jordan 13 Retro GS ‘Wheat’ brings back a two-tone colorway originally released in 2004. The upper features white leather construction on the shoe’s dimpled overlays and toe, along with beige suede paneling that extends from the midfoot and around the heel. A green-tinted holograph ‘eye’ adorns the lateral collar, while an embroidered Jumpman graces the tongue. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a white Phylon midsole, partially wrapped in beige synthetic suede and supported by a panther-paw rubber outsole.

Nike Air Footscape Woven PRM Black Croc (Women's)
Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft Medium Olive (TD)
results.story: The Air Jordan 4 Retro SE TD ‘Craft’ in ‘Olive’ carries a nubuck and suede upper in varying shades of drab green. Black leather is utilized on the support wings, stitched eyelets, and Jumpman-branded heel tab. A second Jumpman logo adorns the tongue. In lieu of traditional TPU netting, the quarter panel features suede construction in an embossed grid pattern. The sneaker sits atop a white foam midsole, reinforced by a two-tone rubber outsole in black and grey.

results.name: Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft Medium Olive (GS)
results.story: Made for big kids, the Air Jordan 4 Retro SE GS Craft in ‘Olive’ features a layered upper in nubuck and suede. Quarter panels are updated with embossed suede in a gridded pattern, replacing the TPU netting of the original. Contrasting black accents settle on the shoe’s leather support wings, molded eyelets and textile collar lining. A cream-colored Jumpman logo adorns the woven tongue tag and semi-translucent back tab. Undergirding the sneaker is a lightweight foam midsole with visible Air-sole cushioning.

results.name: Nike Terminator Low PRM Black Croc
results.story: The Nike Terminator Low ‘Black Croc’ updates the leather upper with a subtle off-white base, contrasted by croc-textured black leather on the signature Swoosh, forefoot overlay and back tab. A woven Nike tag adorns the tongue, while an oversized Nike wordmark wraps around the back heel. The low-top rests on a rubber cupsole that pairs aged sidewalls with a black herringbone-traction outsole.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low Red Stardust (Women's)
results.story: The Nike Women’s Dunk Low ‘Red Stardust’ channels vintage hoops style, highlighted by a white leather upper with dusty rose overlays at the forefoot and heel. Rugged Orange accents settle on the collar lining and signature Swoosh. Additional branding elements take the form of a woven Nike tongue tag and an embroidered Nike wordmark on the back tab. The sneaker sits atop a sturdy rubber cupsole, featuring stitched sidewall construction and an interior foam wedge.

results.name: Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft Medium Olive (PS)
results.story: Built for little kids, the Air Jordan 4 Retro SE GS Craft in ‘Olive’ makes use of a layered upper in a tonal blend of nubuck and suede. The quarter panel discards the TPU netting of the original in favor of embossed suede in a gridded pattern. Black textile lines the collar, matching the eyelets and leather support wings. A cream-hued Jumpman logo adorns the tongue and semi-translucent back tab. The mid-top rests on a white foam midsole, supported by a herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

Jordan 5 Retro A Ma Maniére Dawn (Women's)
results.story: Launching as part of a two-piece collaborative pack, the A Ma Maniére x Women’s Air Jordan 5 Retro ‘Dawn’ sports a pale grey leather upper, revised with a slimmed-down collar and pre-yellowed quarter panel netting formed with A Ma Maniére’s ‘A’ logo. Additional branding elements include an embroidered ‘23’ on the lateral heel, Nike Air branding on the back heel, and mismatched Jumpman and ‘A’ logos on each silver reflective tongue. Blue shark tooth detailing enlivens a black polyurethane midsole with visible Air-sole cushioning in the heel. A pre-aged translucent rubber outsole features a herringbone traction pattern for optimal grip.

Nike Mac Attack SP Social Status Summit White
results.story: The Social Status x Nike Mac Attack SP ‘Summit White’ showcases a breathable mesh upper with a 3M reflective underlay. A forefoot overlay in ivory suede is contrasted by black leather detailing on the collar and heel counter. Woven green tongue tags display mismatched Nike and Social Status branding, while custom insoles list Social Status’ retail locations. The sneaker rests on a durable cupsole, featuring vintage off-white sidewalls and a grippy black rubber outsole.

Nike Zoom LeBron 2 LX Beast
results.story: Based on a 2014 PE colorway that was never released to the public, the Nike Zoom LeBron 2 ‘Beast’ showcases a hairy upper in a mix of cheetah and zebra prints. Crimson accents stand out on the branding elements, which include an embroidered Swoosh on the removable ankle strap and LeBron James’ signature on the lateral heel. The sneaker rests on a blacked-out midsole with springy Zoom Air cushioning in the forefoot and heel. A white rubber outsole provides durable traction underfoot.

Vans Sk8-Hi EXT Advisory Board Crystals Black White
results.story: The Advisory Board Crystals x Vans Sk8-Hi EXT ‘Black White’ reunites the partner brands on a mixed-material design, highlighted by asymmetrical color blocking in neutral white, off-white and black tones. Secured with toggle lacing, the upper features a combination of suede, leather, textile and mesh. The shortened collar reveals an exposed foam lining, along with a mesh interior sleeve for a snug fit. Webbing pull tabs are added to the heel and tongue, the latter marked with dual Vans and Abc. branding. Underfoot, a waffle-tread outsole in gum rubber provides grippy traction.

results.name: Sean Wotherspoon x Gazelle Indoor 'Green Hemp'
Nice Kicks x Samba 'Consortium Cup'
results.story: The Nice Kicks x adidas Samba ‘Consortium Cup’ is taken from a collaborative collection that brings together the Three Stripes with leading retail partners. This elevated take on the classic silhouette features an off-white leather upper with tonal suede construction on the forefoot overlay and back tab. Textile trim with raw edges outlines the eyestay and signature three-stripes. ‘Nice Kicks’ is stamped in gold-foil lettering on the lateral quarter panel, while dual branding appears on each tongue and sockliner. A gum rubber cupsole anchors the low-profile model.

Jordan 3 Retro Off Noir
results.story: The Women’s Air Jordan 3 Retro ‘Off Noir’ delivers a black nubuck upper with grey elephant print overlays at the forefoot and heel. Black perforated leather appears on the eyestay and padded collar, while molded eyelets are rendered in a contrasting off-white finish. Standard Jumpman branding decorates the tongue and back heel. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a two-tone polyurethane midsole with an exposed Air-sole unit nestled in the heel.
